1097
01:32:37,414 --> 01:32:39,495
The Guerrilla Team.

1098
01:32:43,466 --> 01:32:46,887
Wolfenstein II, the New Colossus,

1099
01:32:46,887 --> 01:32:51,649
developed by Machine Games, published by Bethesda Softworks.

1100
01:32:51,649 --> 01:33:01,413
Jens Mappes, Joerg Gustafsson, Tommy Tordtsen-Bjork.

1101
01:33:01,413 --> 01:33:05,194
