1175
01:40:22,839 --> 01:40:31,364
I am thankful for those who created and worked in this medium and industry long before I

1176
01:40:31,364 --> 01:40:32,205
was part of it.

1177
01:40:32,205 --> 01:40:35,907
For creating a medium that I fell in love with decades ago.

1178
01:40:37,174 --> 01:40:41,017
for nurturing a culture of sharing and self-improvement,

1179
01:40:41,017 --> 01:40:45,221
and for working on improving this industry,

1180
01:40:45,221 --> 01:40:47,223
tiny step by tiny step.

1181
01:40:47,223 --> 01:40:48,904
I will try to uphold those values,

1182
01:40:48,904 --> 01:40:50,886
and I will try to improve upon that

1183
01:40:50,886 --> 01:40:53,008
which you would not or could not.

1184
01:40:54,717 --> 01:40:59,818
I'm thankful to everyone who took a chance on me, and there are many of you from my early

1185
01:40:59,818 --> 01:41:02,539
