1186
01:41:02,539 --> 01:41:06,780
I'm very aware that I'm far from perfect and that many of you have worked hard to support

1187
01:41:06,780 --> 01:41:13,181
me, teach me, correct me, work around or with my idiosyncrasies, and help me do what I do.

1188
01:41:13,181 --> 01:41:18,983
I'm thankful to my co-founder, JW, who despite our well-documented differences...

1189
01:41:24,830 --> 01:41:29,093
who despite our well documented differences has always been a person I'm thankful to work with

1190
01:41:29,093 --> 01:41:37,859
and who has, without exception or reservation, supported me using Flamberg's time, brand and resources to help other developers

1191
01:41:37,859 --> 01:41:40,842
and pushes me to stand up for what I believe is right.

1192
01:41:40,842 --> 01:41:44,684
I'm thankful to my wife, Adriaan.

1193
01:41:53,138 --> 01:41:57,260
Who I met through games, who proposed to me through games,

1194
01:41:57,260 --> 01:42:01,322
and who has, through support and example,

1195
01:42:01,322 --> 01:42:04,963
shown to me what it means to be a gracious, considerate,

1196
01:42:04,963 --> 01:42:09,145
and inspiring human first, and a hardworking, generous,

1197
01:42:09,145 --> 01:42:10,886
and responsible creator second.

1198
01:42:10,886 --> 01:42:13,907
Her generosity and thoughtfulness

1199
01:42:13,907 --> 01:42:15,068
are a daily inspiration.

1200
01:42:16,493 --> 01:42:20,396
I'm thankful to the passionate players around the world, those that support this medium

1201
01:42:20,396 --> 01:42:24,659
with their passion, their kindness, their constructive criticism, their curiosity, and

1202
01:42:24,659 --> 01:42:27,861
their love for this medium and its creators.

1203
01:42:27,861 --> 01:42:33,024
Your enthusiasm is an inspiration, a goal to work towards, and a reward all at once.

1204
01:42:34,617 --> 01:42:39,538
I'm thankful for the designers, the programmers, the artists, the musicians, the actors, sound

1205
01:42:39,538 --> 01:42:45,660
designers, writers, QA, localizers, platforms, publishers, press, critics, content creators,

1206
01:42:45,660 --> 01:42:51,301
marketeers, investors, producers, and other people that touched games on their way from

1207
01:42:51,301 --> 01:42:55,322
the tiniest concept to the curious input and hearts of a player.

1208
01:42:55,322 --> 01:43:03,164
You are all part of what allows this medium to flourish, and this medium is better for

1209
01:43:03,164 --> 01:43:04,205
having you be part of it.

1210
01:43:05,870 --> 01:43:10,993
I am thankful for the event organizers, community organizers, teachers and professors, government

1211
01:43:10,993 --> 01:43:16,477
employees, archivists, activists, researchers, and other passionate people sacrificing part

1212
01:43:16,477 --> 01:43:23,202
of their life towards helping this industry and community connect and grow.

1213
01:43:23,202 --> 01:43:28,126
Without your passion and efforts, I would not be able to visit your communities, to

1214
01:43:28,126 --> 01:43:33,110
learn from your cities, your cultures, and your country's unique stories, challenges,

1215
01:43:33,110 --> 01:43:34,030
and opportunities.

1216
01:43:36,272 --> 01:43:44,700
I am thankful for those that work and fight to democratize this medium, to stand against

1217
01:43:44,700 --> 01:43:50,606
