1235
01:45:38,723 --> 01:45:43,385
upon that which we here today will not or cannot.

1236
01:45:43,385 --> 01:45:50,266
Being an ambassador of something can only be a point of pride if you believe that that

1237
01:45:50,266 --> 01:45:52,227
