1675
02:19:06,528 --> 02:19:10,310
Psychonauts 2 in production now, and Broken Age,

1676
02:19:10,310 --> 02:19:15,052
and even pay it forward by helping other smaller developers through Double Fine Presents.

1677
02:19:19,805 --> 02:19:25,430
Tonight it is my great honor to present GDC's Lifetime Achievement Award to a friend who's

1678
02:19:25,430 --> 02:19:30,415
built some of this industry's most memorable and new experiences, and on a personal level

1679
02:19:30,415 --> 02:19:34,519
has helped inspire me to devote my career to celebrating games and the people who make

1680
